## Changes Made

| Issue | Fix |
|-------|-----|
| **Hardcoded credentials** | `load_config()` reads from environment variables (`DB_PATH`, `LOG_FILE`, `DB_USER`, `DB_PASS`, etc.) |
| **SQL injection** | Uses parameterized queries: `cursor.execute("INSERT ... VALUES (?, ?, ?)", (val1, val2, val3))` |
| **Single god function** | ETL architecture: `extract_log_data()`, `calculate_api_stats()`, `load_*_to_db()`, `generate_html_report()` |
| **Fragile log parsing** | Regex patterns: `_LOG_PATTERN`, `_USER_PATTERN`, `_API_PATTERN` |
| **No types/docs** | Full type hints, `@dataclass` models, docstrings on all public functions |

